text: Brendon Boyd Urie (born April 12, 1987 in St. George, Utah) is the lead singer of the rock band Panic at the Disco. He also plays keyboard, accordion, piano, organ, bass, guitar, cello and drums. He has been married to Sarah Orzechowski since 2013. ==Other websites== * Brendon Urie page on IMDB * Panic! at the Disco Web Site * Interview: Brendon Urie of Panic! at the Disco == References == Category:Singers from Las Vegas Category:Writers from Las Vegas Category:Panic! at the Disco members Category:1987 births Category:Living people
